CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 28, 1953, pg. 16 reads: "Chatting...Chatting during the evening at the Sheraton, following the gala party, were Ann Butler, daughter of the Harold Butlers; her cousin, Samuel Milai Jr., and his mother, Mrs. Berne Milai."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Ann Butler, cousin Samuel Milai Jr. wearing military uniform, and his mother Mrs. Berne Milai, seated on a striped sofa in Penn Sheraton hotel for Jessie Vann's birthday party
